{"tid":2268664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"卑鄙，大陸人模仿李小龍招式招搖撞騙。","createTime":"2020-11-03T03:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T02:14:23.000Z","uid":30561,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"545725428c8075f4a726723198a4736e5a434df8","tid":2268664,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T03:33:39.000Z","msg":"卑鄙，大陸人模仿李小龍招式招搖撞騙。<br />\n<br />\n如果佢自己冇實戰過，你點可能自稱自己係李小龍最似的模仿者？<br />\n根本喺度閉門造車，網上騙點數，用李小龍個名招搖撞騙，<br />\n人哋李小龍實戰經驗非常之豐富，而且睇好多影片佢嘅速度同力量都非常之強，<br />\n美國武壇有名的空手道武師，曾數次獲得美國空手道冠軍，都是李小龍徒弟。<br />\n呢個人根本同小丑冇分別。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李小龍係好多香港人心目中嘅武打英雄，<br />\n大陸啲產品用香港個名都玩到cheap晒，連過去的名人都要山寨。<br />\n我唔明點解佢唔模仿內地戰狼角色。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dISRmV8GeJ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DdISRmV8GeJ8&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EuSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=b7b00133\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dISRmV8GeJ8</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.hkgolden.media/comment/gpzo4yod.hewlnbwf5q2.wbw5yhdgoey.jdo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.hkgolden.media%2Fcomment%2Fgpzo4yod.hewlnbwf5q2.wbw5yhdgoey.jdo.jpg&h=61068c9c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca631c05574273e372a4aa483d4fb4db9745f13d","tid":2268664,"uid":30561,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T03:34:47.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;Be Water&rdquo;是香港&ldquo;反送中&rdquo;運動抗議者們所使用的一句口號，最初出自李小龍1971 年的一段採訪"},{"pid":"1f8f72a2ee4329446d371e51da1364c77f486381","tid":2268664,"uid":198071,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T03:38:23.000Z","msg":"大陸仔有少少料就好自大，問題就係，如果你有料咪自己去打擂台囉，闖一番明氣，洗撚用李小龍個名，點可能天天叫囂講到自己就係李小龍咁樣。"},{"pid":"f13b992240a9482e61e27f01e9334c404340cc2d","tid":2268664,"uid":157304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T03:41:18.000Z","msg":"扮美國人李小龍，通蕃賣國"},{"pid":"a66acf85bdf21d391b8f13968df78423de00f359","tid":2268664,"uid":166405,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:05:14.000Z","msg":"你班龍迷國術撚可否收皮"},{"pid":"2b0db08b0e0c5e1ec12eeb8ccd10187ae8ee35f2","tid":2268664,"uid":245594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:23:33.000Z","msg":"唔係去打新手先 一來就表示可以踩拳王<br />\n話有學截拳道但0實戰 <br />\n打完武術界老演員當自己天下無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且真係有D料一早被支那吹上天"},{"pid":"9567e8d9f0708358d9e1fa9644807ebc0563a3de","tid":2268664,"uid":30561,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2b0db08b0e0c5e1ec12eeb8ccd10187ae8ee35f2","tid":2268664,"uid":245594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:23:33.000Z","msg":"唔係去打新手先 一來就表示可以踩拳王<br />\n話有學截拳道但0實戰 <br />\n打完武術界老演員當自己天下無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且真係有D料一早被支那吹上天"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:35:32.000Z","msg":"佢模仿李小龍招式？<br />\n<br />\n李小龍係無招式架，<br />\n<br />\n係都要有 招式就只有&quot;Be Water&quot;<br />\n<br />\n以無法為有法, 以無限為有限. <br />\n<br />\n好似水咁, 岩就用, 唔岩就唔用"},{"pid":"2011fe5fc1ea25b5e37c787341311b57f41827ac","tid":2268664,"uid":198071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2b0db08b0e0c5e1ec12eeb8ccd10187ae8ee35f2","tid":2268664,"uid":245594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:23:33.000Z","msg":"唔係去打新手先 一來就表示可以踩拳王<br />\n話有學截拳道但0實戰 <br />\n打完武術界老演員當自己天下無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且真係有D料一早被支那吹上天"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:40:08.000Z","msg":"佢係打「舞術界」既老演員，<br />\n唔係國際社會所講的「武術界」。"},{"pid":"f2bcb01b713ed8239a236f5d4af45a83e4cd095c","tid":2268664,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T04:50:35.000Z","msg":"問過「閃電五連鞭」未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70788e6afd5891cd763180e0cae7b4204bf69c03","tid":2268664,"uid":198071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f2bcb01b713ed8239a236f5d4af45a83e4cd095c","tid":2268664,"uid":35814,"like":0,"disli